vote.title: Authorize (1) a five-year service contract for benefits consulting services and auditing services of medical and pharmacy benefit plans for the Department of Human Resources in an amount not to exceed $1,143,750.00; and (2) the ratification for the Department of Human Resources to pay outstanding invoices in the amount of $162,895.81 for benefits consulting services and auditing services of medical and pharmacy benefit plans - Holmes Murphy and Associates, LLC, most advantageous proposer of eight - Total not to exceed $1,306,645.81 - Financing: Employee Benefits Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
